          "Core introduced the subjunctive. Now",
          "let's master the triggers. The pattern:",
          "Main clause + QUE + subjunctive clause",
          "",
          "WISHES/REQUESTS:                     Press 1",
          "Quiero que vengas.",
          "(I want you to come.)",
          "Te pido que me ayudes.",
          "(I ask you to help me.)",
          "",
          "EMOTIONS:                            Press 2",
          "Me alegra que estés aquí.",
          "(I'm glad you're here.)",
          "Es triste que no pueda venir.",
          "(It's sad he/she can't come.)",
          "",
          "KEY: Two different subjects.",
          "Quiero comer = I want to eat (no subj.)"
