          "",
          "No creo que sea verdad.",
          "(I don't think it's true.)",
          "Dudo que lo sepa.",
          "(I doubt he/she knows it.)",
          "",
          "SUBJUNCTIVE TRIGGER PHRASES:",
          "",
          "es importante que... (it's important)",
