          "",
          "PASSIVE: ser + participle (action)   Press 1",
          "La casa fue construida en 1990.",
          "(The house was built in 1990.)",
          "",
          "RESULT: estar + participle (state)   Press 2",
          "La puerta está cerrada.",
          "(The door is closed.)",
          "",
          "La ventana fue rota por el niño.     Press 3",
          "(The window was broken by the child.)",
          "La ventana está rota.",
          "(The window is broken.)",
          "",
          "Ser = the breaking happened (event)",
          "Estar = it's in a broken state (now)"
